definitions.definition: An additional one of the same kind.
examples: This napkin fell to the floor, could you please bring me another ?
There is one sterling and here is another

definitions.definition: One that is different from the current one.
examples: I saw one movie, but I think I will see another .

definitions.definition: One of a group of things of the same kind.
examples: His interests keep shifting from one thing to another .

main_definition: An additional one of the same kind.
secondary_definitions: One that is different from the current one.
One of a group of things of the same kind.
